    <briefdescription>
<para>Generic header for encoded ADC streaming frames. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This packed structure is placed at the beginning of each frame produced by the ADC RTIO subsystem. It provides the metadata needed to re-assemble the samples that follow. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
